cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use DAERWEN in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "DAERWEN: Physics-Grounded Ecological Intelligence"
abstract: >-
  DAERWEN (Darwin-inspired Emergent World Engine) is a research platform
  exploring how intelligence can emerge from simple physical rules,
  chemical interactions, and genetic evolution, without hardcoded
  behaviors. It is proposed as a subconscious substrate capable of
  running continuously beneath a symbolic (LLM) conscious layer.
